headline: 3 Reasons ITW is Risky and 1 Stock to Buy Instead
summary: Although Illinois Tool Works (currently trading at $260.73 per share) has gained 8.9% over the last six months, it has trailed the S&P 500’s 24.7% return during that period. This might have investors contemplating their next move.
